 id=\"faq-question-1747513000880\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat Units can be evolved in Anime Saga?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eCurrently, you can only evolve \u003cstrong\u003eMythic Units\u003c/strong\u003e in Anime Saga.\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv id=\"faq-question-1747500671991\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCan you sell materials you don’t need in Anime Saga?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eUnfortunately, \u003cstrong\u003eyou can’t sell the excess materials\u003c/strong\u003e that will inevitably pile up in your inventory.\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv id=\"faq-question-1747513096403\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow do you farm evolution materials in Anime Saga?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eYou can farm evolution materials in Anime Saga by completing \u003cstrong\u003eRaids \u003c/strong\u003e(level 25+). Also, if you need a specific one to evolve a Unit right away, you might find it in the \u003cstrong\u003eGold Shop\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003ci data-stringify-type=\"italic\"\u003e The Escapist is supported by our audience. When you purchase through links on our site, we may earn a small affiliate commission. \u003c/i\u003e\u003ci data-stringify-type=\"italic\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/affiliate-policy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-stringify-link=\"https://escapistmagazine.com/affiliate-policy\" data-sk=\"tooltip_parent\"\u003eLearn more about our Affiliate Policy\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\t\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
